```{r load-packages, message = FALSE}
library(tidyverse) 
library(skimr)
library(codebook)
```

```{r load-data, eval=TRUE}
stroke <- read_csv("healthcare_dataset_stroke_data.csv")
```

```{r}
save(stroke,file="./stroke.RData")
```

## Stroke Dataset Codebook
```{r, eval=TRUE}
codebook(stroke)
```

## Skim Stroke Dataset Summary
```{r, eval=TRUE}
skim(stroke)
```
